  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2023-03-10",
    "date": "2023-04-04T14:53:17Z",
    "text": "Daylight All Year Leads to Ideal Gains in Happiness and Temperament Act or the DAYLIGHT Act\n\nThis bill allows states to observe daylight savings time year-round. (States may already choose to observe standard time year-round.)\n\nNo later than two years after enactment of this bill, the Government Accountability Office shall submit a report to Congress containing the results of a study on implementing daylight savings time year-round."
